title: The World Owes You Nothing
itunes:title: The World Owes You Nothing
description:
Episode 476 - When did so many people get the feeling that they "deserve" anything? The people who get the furthest in life are the ones that know that they are not owed anything and that they must work their tails off to get what they want in this life. In this episode, I dive into this topic and talk about how to get whatever it is that you want.
